<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Luggage" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Luggage,</orth> any thing cumbersome to be carried: <cit><quote>to dote thus on such l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.231" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 231</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>bestow your l. where you found it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.298.83" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 298</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>bring your l. on your back,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.160" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 4, 160</bibl></cit>. == the baggage of an army: <bibl n="shak. h5 4.4.80" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 4, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.1" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 1</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>